    <p class="lede" style="margin:0 0 32px;max-width:66ch;">Every New York law-firm engagement follows the same four-phase rhythm &mdash; trust compliance first, clean operating books second, advisory third.</p>
    <div class="r-2">
      {%- for p in process %}
      <article class="dc-card"><span class="eyebrow">{{ p.phase }}</span><h3>{{ p.title | safe }}</h3><div class="prose" style="font-size:15px;"><p>{{ p.body | safe }}</p></div></article>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── ADVISORY · standing brand line (pull-quote .statement). (H2: Clean trust accounting is the floor. Running a profitable firm is the point.) ── #}
<section class="sec reveal" id="ny-ind-legal-advisory" style="background:var(--color-paper-warm);border-top:1px solid var(--border-subtle);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
  <div class="ct read">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">Beyond the books</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
